        "@value": "DEFINITION: Relates a child category to a parent category in an informal (e.g., faceted) hierarchy."
      },
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string",
        "@value": "EXAMPLE: Refrigerator handles are not refrigerators, but it may be useful to represent their relationship hierarchically for a faceted UI filter."
      }
